headline: 4 Manufacturing Electronics Stocks to Consider on Promising Industry Trends
summary: The Zacks Manufacturing - Electronics industry gains from strength across major end markets. ETN, EMR, FELE and POWL are some notable stocks in the industry.

headline: 3 Industrials Stocks That Fall Short
summary: Even if they go mostly unnoticed, industrial businesses are the backbone of our country. Their momentum is also rising as lower interest rates have incentivized higher capital spending. As a result, the industry has posted a 36% gain over the past six months, beating the S&P 500 by 13.2 percentage points.
